            "body": "I also noticed while trying to get a minimal repro this afternoon that spinning curl against the nginxhello image running in a pod would get recv failures and block intermittently. I'm not sure if this is the same behaviour because after about 10-20 seconds, it'll come back.\n\nIf someone could drop some handy tips for how I might be able to get some logging out of the rootlessport process, that might make it easier to track down what's going on."
